g.text: The Bedrock of Machine Learning

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: The performance of your ML system is ultimately limited by the quality of its data.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Fixing a data problem is often more valuable than finding a better algorithm.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Common Data Problems

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Bias: The data is not a true representation of the real

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: world. For example, a facial recognition model trained

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: primarily on light-skinned faces will perform poorly on dark-

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: skinned faces.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Unbiased & Representative: The data reflects the

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: diversity and distribution of the real-world environment

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: where the model will be deployed.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Poor Quality & Noise: Data contains errors, missing

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: values, or random corruptions. For example, a user enters

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: "N/A" in an age field, or a sensor provides a faulty

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: reading due to a power spike.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Clean & Consistent: The data is well-formatted, with clear,

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: consistent labels and a low rate of errors or missing

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: values.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Low Predictive Signal: The available data doesn't contain

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: the information needed to make the desired prediction. For

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: example, trying to predict a customer's lifetime value using

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: only their sign-up date.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Informative: The data contains features that are

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: highly correlated with the target outcome. It has

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: the necessary signal to solve the problem.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Imbalance: One class is vastly overrepresented. A fraud

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: model trained on 99.9% non-fraudulent transactions may

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: struggle to learn the patterns of the rare 0.1% of

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: fraudulent cases.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Good Coverage & Sufficiently Large: There are enough

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: examples for all important subgroups and classes,

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: especially the rare cases, for the model to learn from.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Inconsistent Labels: The same type of example is given

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: different labels. For example, one annotator labels a

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: support ticket "Billing Issue" while another labels an

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: identical ticket "Payment Problem."

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Clear & Consistent Labeling: The labels are

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: unambiguous and applied according to a well-defined

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: and consistent schema.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Feedback Loop Contamination: The data was generated

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: by a previous version of the model, creating a self-

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: reinforcing bias. For example, a recommendation system

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: only gets click data on items it recommends.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Independent of the Model: The ground-truth data is

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: generated independently of the model's own

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: predictions, ensuring it reflects real-world truth, not

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: the model's biases.

g.text: The Data Leakage

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: When information from outside the training data accidentally contaminates the training process. The model learns a

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: signal that will not be available when it makes predictions in the real world.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Data leakage creates a model that looks phenomenally good during offline evaluation but completely fails in production.
